From af5209439dc8c1a95325ec7b68aea3998fe31734 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Wed, 10 Jun 2026 13:35:26 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add mobile PWA app with bottom navigation and smartphone
 features

- Add manifest.json, service worker, and app icons for installable PWA
- Bottom navigation (Kalender, Heute, +, Kunden, Mehr) with slide-out menu
- Mobile-optimized topbar, bottom-sheet modals, safe-area insets
- GPS location button for pickup/destination address fields
- Native share API fallback before WhatsApp on mobile
- Install banner and README instructions for home screen setup
